WEBVTT

00:01.581 --> 00:02.583
PREVIOUSLY ON "REVENGE"...

00:02.583 --> 00:03.674
LET'S
GET DOWN TO BUSINESS,

00:03.674 --> 00:04.795
PROVIDED I CAN BE SURE
YOU'RE AN ALLY.

00:04.795 --> 00:05.796
AN INTRIGUING OFFER.

00:05.796 --> 00:06.757
YOU'VE GOT A DEAL.

00:06.757 --> 00:08.007
WHAT'S GOING ON?

00:08.007 --> 00:09.090
JACK. I'M SORRY.

00:09.090 --> 00:11.132
I'M TAKING YOU HOME
TO L.A., OKAY?

00:11.132 --> 00:14.765
MY LAWYER SENT OVER
OUR BUSINESS CONTRACT.

00:14.765 --> 00:17.188
WHY DOES THIS SAY THAT YOU PLAN
TO OWN 70% OF THE COMPANY?

00:17.188 --> 00:19.730
ANY OTHER INVESTOR
WOULD ASK FOR MUCH MORE.

00:19.730 --> 00:21.192
MAYBE I SHOULD
FIND OUT FOR MYSELF.

00:21.192 --> 00:22.563
I KNOW SOMEONE
WHO CAN HELP YOU.

00:22.563 --> 00:23.944
WHO?
 MY BROTHER.

00:23.944 --> 00:25.526
MY FATHER IS GROOMING ME

00:25.526 --> 00:27.238
TO TAKE OVER
THE LeMARCHAL EMPIRE.

00:27.238 --> 00:28.819
WE'LL MAKE A GREAT TEAM,
DANIEL.

00:28.819 --> 00:31.322
THIS TABLE IS THE LAST THING
MY FATHER AND I WORKED ON.

00:31.322 --> 00:32.573
"OSCAR CHAPMAN."

00:32.573 --> 00:33.784
WHO IS THAT?

00:33.784 --> 00:36.157
CHAPMAN WORKED
FOR LeMARCHAL MEDIA IN '93.

00:36.157 --> 00:37.118
DIED IN A CAR ACCIDENT.

00:37.118 --> 00:38.119
ANOTHER DEAD END.

00:38.119 --> 00:39.870
HEY, NOLAN.
WHAT?

00:39.870 --> 00:42.163
OSCAR CHAPMAN
FAKED HIS OWN DEATH.

00:42.163 --> 00:43.714
THEN WE BETTER PRAY
WE CAN FIND HIM.

00:46.127 --> 00:48.089
Announcer: AND THEY'RE OFF!

00:48.089 --> 00:52.012
Emily: VICTORY
 CAN NEVER BE ACHIEVED ALONE.

00:52.012 --> 00:57.098
ALLEGIANCES MUST BE FORGED
 TO OVERCOME SUPERIOR FORCES --

00:57.098 --> 01:00.561
SOME BORN FROM A SHARED GOAL,

01:00.561 --> 01:03.604
OTHERS OUT OF DESPERATE NEED.

01:03.604 --> 01:07.858
BUT FOR A UNION TO SUCCEED,

01:07.858 --> 01:10.241
ONE MUST DETERMINE
IF AN ALLY IS TRULY A FRIEND...

01:12.403 --> 01:14.655
...OR MERELY AN ENEMY
 IN DISGUISE.

01:14.655 --> 01:16.997
[ CAMERA SHUTTER CLICKING ]

01:16.997 --> 01:17.998
YOU CAME.

01:17.998 --> 01:20.461
I'M SURPRISED.

01:20.461 --> 01:22.873
AS WAS I WHEN I RECEIVED
YOUR INVITATION.

01:22.873 --> 01:25.336
IT'S BEEN A WHILE
SINCE WE LAST SPOKE.

01:25.336 --> 01:27.798
I WAS BEGINNING TO THINK
YOU LOST INTEREST

01:27.798 --> 01:29.170
IN WHAT I HAD TO SAY.

01:29.170 --> 01:34.175
I ALWAYS WANT TO HEAR
THE THOUGHTS OF BEAUTIFUL WOMEN.

01:34.175 --> 01:35.426
[ LAUGHS ]

01:35.426 --> 01:38.219
ESPECIALLY ONES
WITH SECRETS ON THE GRAYSONS.

01:38.219 --> 01:41.392
CONRAD'S LANDED SOME IMPRESSIVE
BLOWS AGAINST YOU.

01:41.392 --> 01:44.395
I ASSUME YOU WANT ME
TO HELP CLIP HIS WINGS?

01:44.395 --> 01:46.897
YOU SAID YOU POSSESS LEVERAGE
ON HIM?

01:48.229 --> 01:49.820
I'LL PAY A LOT FOR IT.

01:49.820 --> 01:52.323
[ SIGHS ]
WELL, IT'S AN ATTRACTIVE OFFER,

01:52.323 --> 01:54.945
CONSIDERING
MY CURRENT FINANCIAL STATE.

01:54.945 --> 01:57.408
BUT SURELY YOU HAVE OTHER
AVENUES YOU CAN PURSUE.

01:57.408 --> 01:58.739
NONE WITH YOUR ACCESS.

01:58.739 --> 02:00.080
WELL, THAT'S FUNNY,

02:00.080 --> 02:02.913
SEEING AS YOUR NEW PARTNER
WAS MARRIED TO HIM

02:02.913 --> 02:04.165
FOR OVER 20 YEARS.

02:06.297 --> 02:09.250
WHICH MEANS
YOU'RE PLAYING ME.

02:11.050 --> 02:13.464
TELL VICTORIA,
"NICE TRY."

02:13.464 --> 02:17.258
[ RACE ANNOUNCER
SPEAKING INDISTINCTLY ]

02:17.258 --> 02:20.140
[ CHEERS AND APPLAUSE ]

02:20.140 --> 02:23.764
HMM, WHAT DO YOU KNOW,
I WON.

02:23.764 --> 02:25.145
Aiden:
I'M PAST SECURITY

02:25.145 --> 02:27.438
AND ALMOST AT
THE LeMARCHAL RECORDS ROOM.

02:27.438 --> 02:30.821
I TRUST YOUR MEETING WITH PASCAL
WAS FRUITFUL.

02:30.821 --> 02:34.275
AS I SUSPECTED, VICTORIA
IS USING HIM TO SPY ON ME.

02:34.275 --> 02:36.537
WHILE YOU USED HIM
FOR OUR OWN PURPOSE.

02:36.537 --> 02:38.539
The plans were right.

02:38.539 --> 02:41.081
THE MOST SECURE ROOMS
IN THE LeMARCHAL BUILDING

02:41.081 --> 02:43.163
are activated
by Pascal's print.

02:43.163 --> 02:45.706
WELL, THEN,
I'VE GOT WHAT YOU NEED.

02:45.706 --> 02:47.047
[ CELLPHONE BEEPS ]

02:49.340 --> 02:52.253
NOLAN'S PROGRAM
JUST FINISHED LIFTING IT.

02:52.253 --> 02:53.884
I'M TRANSMITTING NOW.

02:55.296 --> 02:56.507
[ CELLPHONE BEEPS ]

03:01.352 --> 03:03.013
[ BEEPS, DOOR BUZZES ]

03:03.013 --> 03:05.356
I'M IN.

03:05.356 --> 03:06.767
Let's just hope
there's something in here

03:06.767 --> 03:08.269
THAT PROVES
OSCAR CHAPMAN IS ALIVE.

03:12.313 --> 03:13.774
JAVIER!

03:13.774 --> 03:16.237
WAKE UP!

03:17.408 --> 03:19.490
CHECKING TO SEE
IF I SNUCK OUT?

03:19.490 --> 03:20.701
I SAID I WOULDN'T.

03:20.701 --> 03:22.953
NO. I TRUST YOU.

03:22.953 --> 03:25.626
BUT CAN WE JUST TALK ABOUT
WHAT HAPPENED THE OTHER DAY?

03:27.288 --> 03:29.290
[ SIGHS ]
COME ON, PAL.

03:29.290 --> 03:31.792
I THINK I'VE EARNED
FIVE MINUTES.

03:31.792 --> 03:34.255
OKAY.

03:34.255 --> 03:36.337
WE'LL TALK LATER.

03:41.392 --> 03:43.934
[ LAUGHS ]
THAT WAS A CLOSE ONE.

03:43.934 --> 03:46.186
DO YOU THINK
HE KNOWS I'M HERE?

03:46.186 --> 03:48.228
AND WHAT'S HE GONNA DO?

03:48.228 --> 03:49.310
GROUND ME?

03:49.310 --> 03:51.692
WELL, HE'S OBVIOUSLY
TRYING TO GUILT YOU

03:51.692 --> 03:53.023
INTO SIGNING WITH HIM.

03:53.023 --> 03:54.405
[ SIGHS ]

03:54.405 --> 03:58.619
YOU STILL WANT ME TO GO
WITH YOUR BROTHER, DON'T YOU?

03:58.619 --> 04:00.240
LOOK, I TOLD YOU.

04:00.240 --> 04:04.325
EVEN IF I AM PISSED AT NOLAN,
I CAN'T DO THAT.

04:04.325 --> 04:06.327
IT WOULD CRUSH HIM.

04:06.327 --> 04:09.249
DANIEL CAN MAKE THINGS HAPPEN
THAT NOLAN CAN'T.

04:09.249 --> 04:12.423
WELL, I SORT OF HAVE MY EYE
ON A DIFFERENT GRAYSON.

04:12.423 --> 04:13.834
AND SHE HAS HERS ON

04:13.834 --> 04:16.547
A ONCE-IN-A-LIFETIME
OPPORTUNITY FOR YOU.

04:16.547 --> 04:17.338
[ GROANS ]

04:17.338 --> 04:19.380
HEY, JUST TALK TO HIM.

04:19.380 --> 04:20.841
MM-HMM.
[ LAUGHS ]

04:20.841 --> 04:22.513
AND TRUST ME.

04:22.513 --> 04:27.187
IF IT'S THAT IMPORTANT
TO YOU, OKAY.

04:27.187 --> 04:28.889
SET IT UP.

04:32.192 --> 04:34.895
Daniel:
SO, I'M REELING THIS KID IN...

04:34.895 --> 04:37.898
IT'S ONLY A MATTER OF TIME
BEFORE I CLOSE HIM.

04:37.898 --> 04:40.531
WHAT EXACTLY
DOES THIS MYSTERY PROGRAM DO

04:40.531 --> 04:41.992
THAT IS SO VALUABLE?

04:41.992 --> 04:43.203
WELL,
CHARLOTTE GOT ME A COPY.

04:43.203 --> 04:46.116
HERE, SEE FOR YOURSELF.

04:48.078 --> 04:50.501
IT'S AN AGGREGATE
OF YOUR DIGITAL FOOTPRINT.

04:50.501 --> 04:53.414
BASICALLY, IT ANALYZES
ALL YOUR ONLINE HABITS,

04:53.414 --> 04:57.127
SO IT CAN DIRECT ANYONE TO
YOUR LIKES, NEEDS, AND DESIRES.

04:57.127 --> 04:58.178
WHAT?

04:58.178 --> 04:59.800
[ Laughing ]
I'M NOT JOKING.

04:59.800 --> 05:01.722
ASK YOURSELF SOMETHING.
TEST IT.

05:01.722 --> 05:03.093
UH, OKAY.

05:03.093 --> 05:04.805
OKAY, MARGAUX,

05:04.805 --> 05:06.807
WHAT SHOES DO I WANT
THIS SEASON?

05:06.807 --> 05:08.268
[ BEEPS ]

05:08.268 --> 05:12.192
JEROME C. ROUSSEAU
 GOLD ANIMAL PEEP TOE PUMPS.

05:12.192 --> 05:14.314
OH, MY GOD.
SHE'S RIGHT.

05:14.314 --> 05:15.896
OF COURSE SHE IS.
SHE'S YOU.

05:15.896 --> 05:16.937
[ LAUGHS ]

05:16.937 --> 05:20.150
HEY, THAT JAVIER
IS A GENIUS.

05:20.150 --> 05:21.942
ARE YOU SURE YOU WANT
TO BRING THIS TO MY FATHER?

05:21.942 --> 05:24.365
LOOK.
WE WANT TO WORK TOGETHER, RIGHT?

05:24.365 --> 05:26.076
BUT YOUR FATHER'S
NOT GONNA LET ME

05:26.076 --> 05:27.498
AS LONG AS MY LAST NAME'S
GRAYSON.

05:27.498 --> 05:30.250
UNLESS, YOU BRING HIM
SOMETHING LIKE THIS.

05:30.250 --> 05:33.163
AND A DEAL LIKE THIS

05:33.163 --> 05:35.165
CHANGES US
FROM SPECTATORS...

05:35.165 --> 05:36.296
[ HORSE WHINNIES ]

05:36.296 --> 05:39.219
...TO OWNERS.

05:42.132 --> 05:45.726
WELL, HELLO, THERE,
VICTORIA.

05:45.726 --> 05:48.679
EMILY,
WHAT AN UNPLEASANT SURPRISE.

05:48.679 --> 05:50.731
I HIGHLY DOUBT THAT,
CONSIDERING THE LITTLE CHAT

05:50.731 --> 05:52.893
THAT YOU ARRANGED BETWEEN ME
AND YOUR NEW PARAMOUR.

05:52.893 --> 05:57.027
OH, I SEE THAT YOUR IMAGINATION
IS AS VIVID AS EVER.

05:58.779 --> 06:00.901
I WOULD LOVE
TO STAY AND CHAT,

06:00.901 --> 06:03.444
BUT I HAVE LESS BORING PEOPLE
TO TALK TO.

06:06.827 --> 06:09.249
WHAT THE HELL
ARE YOU DOING HERE?

06:09.249 --> 06:11.251
YOU AGREED TO STAY AWAY.

06:11.251 --> 06:13.954
RELAX.
THIS ISN'T ABOUT YOU.

06:13.954 --> 06:16.667
I'M IN TOWN TO RECEIVE
THE GREEN AMERICAN AWARD

06:16.667 --> 06:18.549
FOR MY INNOVATION
IN GREEN TECHNOLOGY.

06:18.549 --> 06:21.301
I'M SURPRISED
YOU DIDN'T KNOW.

06:21.301 --> 06:22.673
YOU USED TO BE
SO PLUGGED IN.

06:22.673 --> 06:24.344
LOOK AT YOU,
TRYING TO PROVE

06:24.344 --> 06:26.136
YOU'RE NOT THE SAME
PATHETIC LAPDOG

06:26.136 --> 06:28.058
WHO FOLLOWED CONRAD
AROUND THE OFFICE.

06:28.058 --> 06:30.270
WHAT DO YOU THINK
THESE PEOPLE WOULD THINK

06:30.270 --> 06:32.062
IF THEY KNEW
HOW THE GREAT LUKE GILLIAM

06:32.062 --> 06:33.183
ACQUIRED HIS WEALTH?

06:33.183 --> 06:35.185
YOU'RE REALLY GONNA
BRING THAT UP?

06:40.070 --> 06:42.072
PULL YOURSELF TOGETHER,
VICTORIA.

06:42.072 --> 06:44.655
YOU WERE JUST AS RESPONSIBLE
FOR WHAT HAPPENED.

06:44.655 --> 06:45.736
DON'T PRETEND OTHERWISE.

06:45.736 --> 06:47.788
IT WAS SUPPOSED TO BE YOU,
NOT DAVID.

06:47.788 --> 06:52.372
WELL, UNLIKE HIM, I DIDN'T LET
CONRAD STAB ME IN THE BACK.

06:52.372 --> 06:55.836
HE TRIED TO FRAME ME THE SECOND
HE GOT IN OVER HIS HEAD,

06:55.836 --> 06:58.839
BUT I WAS HAPPY HE DID IT
BECAUSE AT THAT MOMENT,

06:58.839 --> 07:01.251
I LEARNED
THE GREATEST LESSON OF ALL --

07:01.251 --> 07:02.633
SCREW THE OTHER GUY.

07:02.633 --> 07:04.174
CAREFUL, LUKE,

07:04.174 --> 07:07.548
OR YOUR RETURN TO THE HAMPTONS
JUST MIGHT BE YOUR DOWNFALL.

07:07.548 --> 07:09.510
I'D HATE TO MEET
THAT THREAT,

07:09.510 --> 07:14.264
WITH THE EVIDENCE I'VE BEEN
HOLDING ONTO ALL THESE YEARS.

07:14.264 --> 07:15.606
USE IT!

07:15.606 --> 07:17.147
NOTHING
WOULD MAKE ME HAPPIER

07:17.147 --> 07:19.109
THAN TO SEE YOU AND CONRAD
TAKE EACH OTHER DOWN.

07:19.109 --> 07:22.152
YOU NEED TO LEARN
TO LET THE PAST GO.

07:22.152 --> 07:26.066
AFTER ALL,
WE GOT AWAY WITH IT, SCOT-FREE.

07:44.965 --> 07:46.717
Emily:
HIS NAME IS LUKE GILLIAM.

07:46.717 --> 07:48.759
HE WAS GRAYSON GLOBAL'S
BIGGEST EARNER.

07:48.759 --> 07:51.181
RUMOR WAS HE ILLEGALLY
MANIPULATED ENERGY MARKETS,

07:51.181 --> 07:53.644
WHICH CONRAD USED
TO INFLATE PROFITS.

07:53.644 --> 07:55.435
THAT MADE HIM
THE LOGICAL CHOICE

07:55.435 --> 07:57.518
TO TAKE THE FALL
FOR LAUNDERING TERRORIST MONEY.

07:57.518 --> 07:59.690
I MEAN, HE WAS CERTAINLY
AN EASIER SELL THAN YOUR FATHER.

07:59.690 --> 08:01.772
WHEN THAT PLAN FAILED,
THE GRAYSONS HAD NO CHOICE.

08:01.772 --> 08:04.404
BUT I DON'T UNDERSTAND
HOW YOU MISSED GILLIAM BEFORE.

08:04.404 --> 08:06.777
MY FATHER NEVER WROTE ABOUT HIM
IN HIS JOURNALS.

08:06.777 --> 08:08.949
HE QUIT BEFORE THE COMPANY
WAS TIED TO THE BOMBING.

08:08.949 --> 08:10.320
SO, HE JUST TOOK HIS CUT
AND RAN?

08:10.320 --> 08:12.993
HE USED HIS PAYOUT
TO START A NATURAL GAS COMPANY.

08:12.993 --> 08:15.245
HE'S IN TOWN
TO ACCEPT AN AWARD

08:15.245 --> 08:18.038
FOR HIS...
ENVIRONMENTALLY SAFE TECHNIQUES.

08:18.038 --> 08:19.960
YOU HAVE YOUR DOUBTS.
 IT'S MORE THAN THAT.

08:19.960 --> 08:21.832
HE HAS EVIDENCE
ABOUT FLIGHT 197,

08:21.832 --> 08:23.714
AND I'M GOING TO GET IT
FROM HIM.

08:23.714 --> 08:26.426
WHAT ABOUT YOU?

08:26.426 --> 08:30.430
DID YOU FIND ANYTHING IN
OSCAR CHAPMAN'S PERSONNEL FILE?

08:30.430 --> 08:33.472
NO, NO. NOTHING --
WELL, NOTHING CONCRETE.

08:33.472 --> 08:35.054
HE GREW UP IN NEW YORK,

08:35.054 --> 08:37.347
WAS TRANSFERRED TO LONDON
AROUND THE TIME OF THE BOMBING.

08:37.347 --> 08:40.309
IF MASON WAS RIGHT
AND OSCAR FAKED HIS OWN DEATH,

08:40.309 --> 08:43.232
THEN HE MAY HAVE RETURNED HOME
TO HIDE.

08:43.232 --> 08:44.605
I WISH I COULD HELP YOU.

08:44.605 --> 08:45.906
YOU STAY FOCUSED.

08:45.906 --> 08:47.908
GET THAT EVIDENCE.

08:50.320 --> 08:52.322
YOU'RE GONNA
NEED THIS LATER.

08:54.244 --> 08:57.457
WE WANT BIGGER.
WE HAVE TO WOW HIM.

08:57.457 --> 09:00.921
AND MASCULINE COLORS --
RED, ORANGE, BLUE.

09:00.921 --> 09:02.793
[ PHONE RINGING ]
 NOTHING TOO SOFT.

09:02.793 --> 09:04.835
OH,
I GOT NOTHING FOR YOU.

09:04.835 --> 09:07.087
[ LAUGHS ] JACK!
YOU'RE BACK!

09:07.087 --> 09:09.129
YEAH.
I FLEW IN THIS MORNING.

09:09.129 --> 09:10.090
THANKS.

09:10.090 --> 09:13.053
IT'S PRETTY CRAZY
AROUND HERE.

09:13.053 --> 09:18.268
YEAH. I'M JUST ABOUT TO CLOSE
A VERY BIG DEAL WITH DANIEL.

09:20.060 --> 09:21.892
DID YOU HAVE A GOOD TIME
IN L.A.?

09:21.892 --> 09:25.856
WELL, IT WASN'T REALLY
THAT KIND OF TRIP.

09:25.856 --> 09:28.779
MY MOM WAS DEALING WITH
SOME PRETTY HEAVY STUFF.

09:28.779 --> 09:30.110
OH, SURE.

09:30.110 --> 09:31.782
NO, I'M SORRY.

09:31.782 --> 09:33.694
MARGAUX,
CAN YOU LOOK AT THIS?

09:33.694 --> 09:35.696
EXCUSE US.
EXCUSE US.

09:38.458 --> 09:41.331
MARGAUX...
[ SIGHS ]

09:41.331 --> 09:44.665
I GET THAT WHAT YOU'RE
WORKING ON IS REALLY IMPORTANT.

09:44.665 --> 09:46.416
BUT...

09:46.416 --> 09:49.129
I WAS GONE FOR OVER A WEEK,
AND WE DIDN'T TALK ONCE.

09:49.129 --> 09:51.051
WHAT'S GOING ON?

09:51.051 --> 09:55.425
MY FATHER ASKED ME
TO TAKE OVER HIS BUSINESS.

09:55.425 --> 10:00.430
NOT JUST "VOULEZ" --
ALL OF IT.

10:00.430 --> 10:01.481
WOW.

10:04.314 --> 10:08.278
WELL, WE CLEARLY HAVE
A LOT OF STUFF TO CATCH UP ON.

10:08.278 --> 10:11.611
WE NEED TO MAKE TIME
FOR EACH OTHER, MARGAUX.

10:14.444 --> 10:17.497
HOW ABOUT TONIGHT?
HMM?

10:17.497 --> 10:20.410
I GET A SITTER,
WE TURN OFF OUR PHONES,

10:20.410 --> 10:23.413
AND WE TRY TO GET BACK
ON THE SAME PAGE.

10:23.413 --> 10:25.505
UH, YES.
[ CHUCKLES ]

10:25.505 --> 10:27.838
YES.
BUT TONIGHT IS IMPOSSIBLE.

10:27.838 --> 10:31.511
I PROMISE,
ONCE THE DEAL IS DONE,

10:31.511 --> 10:33.383
I'M ALL YOURS.

10:38.558 --> 10:41.972
YOUR HYDRANGEAS ARE DEAD.

10:41.972 --> 10:44.184
TIME WAS
YOU CARED FOR THEM

10:44.184 --> 10:46.646
LIKE THEY WERE GIFTS
FROM CHLORIS HERSELF.

10:46.646 --> 10:49.399
AND YOU'VE NEVER SHOWN
ANY INTEREST IN BOTANY.

10:49.399 --> 10:52.112
SO WHAT DO YOU
REALLY WANT, CONRAD?

10:52.112 --> 10:54.985
WELL, HAMPTONS GOSSIP
IS BUZZING

10:54.985 --> 10:57.117
ABOUT YOUR CONFRONTATION
WITH LUKE GILLIAM.

10:57.117 --> 10:58.448
WE'RE DIVORCED,

10:58.448 --> 11:00.871
AND YOU FORFEITED ANY RIGHT
TO QUESTION MY ACTIONS.

11:00.871 --> 11:02.542
OH, YOU'RE RIGHT.

11:02.542 --> 11:05.085
I'M MERELY HERE
TO PROTECT MY INTERESTS.

11:05.085 --> 11:07.587
I PAID LUKE HANDSOMELY
FOR HIS SILENCE.

11:07.587 --> 11:10.550
AND I'D HATE FOR YOU
TO DERAIL THAT ARMISTICE

11:10.550 --> 11:12.552
WITH YOUR
IRRATIONAL BEHAVIOR.

11:12.552 --> 11:14.795
I COULDN'T BE HAPPIER
TO LEAVE ALL THAT BEHIND

11:14.795 --> 11:17.297
NOW THAT I HAVE TRUE HAPPINESS
ON THE HORIZON.

11:17.297 --> 11:18.508
WITH PASCAL?

11:20.510 --> 11:23.603
I REGRET TO INFORM YOU
THAT YOUR LATEST ROMANTIC FACADE

11:23.603 --> 11:27.517
ISN'T BUILT ON A FOUNDATION
OF HONESTY AND TRUST.

11:27.517 --> 11:30.310
WHY DON'T YOU ASK HIM
ABOUT HIS ROLE

11:30.310 --> 11:34.074
IN THE CONSPIRACY THAT DOOMED
YOUR BELOVED DAVID CLARKE.

11:46.456 --> 11:47.707
GOING SOMEWHERE?

11:47.707 --> 11:50.590
MY PAROLE OFFICER CALLED.

11:50.590 --> 11:52.172
PROBABLY WANTS TO KNOW

11:52.172 --> 11:54.634
WHY I HAVEN'T FOUND
GAINFUL EMPLOYMENT.

11:54.634 --> 11:57.677
MAYBE YOU COULD COME WITH, HUH?
EXPLAIN WHY?

11:57.677 --> 11:59.429
WHY DON'T WE
JUST CLEAR THE AIR?

11:59.429 --> 12:01.431
[ SIGHS ]

12:02.682 --> 12:04.554
WE COULDN'T MAKE A DEAL.
IT'S FINE.

12:04.554 --> 12:05.896
YOU GOT TO WHERE YOU ARE

12:05.896 --> 12:07.938
BY LOOKING OUT
FOR YOUR OWN INTERESTS.

12:07.938 --> 12:12.152
NO, I GOT TO WHERE I AM
BECAUSE SOMEONE BELIEVED IN ME.

12:12.152 --> 12:16.656
OH, YOU MEAN DAVID CLARKE,
THE TERRORIST.

12:16.656 --> 12:18.358
YOU KNOW WHAT?

12:18.358 --> 12:20.861
DESPITE WHAT THE REST
OF THE WORLD THINKS,

12:20.861 --> 12:22.532
HE WAS A GREAT MAN.

12:22.532 --> 12:24.204
DO YOU KNOW SOMETHING
THAT I DON'T?

12:24.204 --> 12:27.788
YEAH, SMARTASS, I DO.

12:27.788 --> 12:33.253
HE SAW IN ME
WHAT I SEE IN YOU --

12:33.253 --> 12:35.505
ANGRY HACKER,

12:35.505 --> 12:37.798
CHIP ON HIS SHOULDER.

12:37.798 --> 12:40.380
YOU HAVE GOT
THE BRILLIANCE,

12:40.380 --> 12:45.265
BUT YOU ALSO HAVE THE POTENTIAL
TO GO DOWN THE WRONG PATH.

12:45.265 --> 12:47.227
YOU MEAN LIKE LETTING
A TERRORIST BANKROLL YOU?

12:47.227 --> 12:50.520
THAT'S WHAT THEY CALLED ME
WHEN WE FIRST MET.

12:50.520 --> 12:52.192
I GOT TO GO.
JUST...

12:53.443 --> 12:55.565
...THINK ABOUT
WHAT I SAID.

12:55.565 --> 12:58.028
YEAH. I WILL.

12:58.028 --> 12:59.399
[ CAR ALARM CHIRPS ]

12:59.399 --> 13:00.951
NOLAN'S GOT A LEAD
ON CHAPMAN.

13:00.951 --> 13:02.492
I'M OFF TO THE CITY
TO MEET HIM NOW.

13:02.492 --> 13:04.244
HOW LONG WILL YOU BE?
 Why?

13:04.244 --> 13:06.076
DO YOU NEED HELP ON YOUR END?
 Nah, don't worry.

13:06.076 --> 13:07.497
I'LL FIGURE SOMETHING OUT.

13:07.497 --> 13:08.618
[ KNOCK ON DOOR ]

13:08.618 --> 13:10.460
I HOPE YOU FIND
WHAT YOU'RE LOOKING FOR.

13:10.460 --> 13:11.621
Okay. Bye.

13:11.621 --> 13:13.413
[ CELLPHONE BEEPS ]

13:17.417 --> 13:19.629
HEY, YOU'RE BACK.

13:19.629 --> 13:21.261
YEAH.

13:21.261 --> 13:22.632
IS THIS A BAD TIME?

13:22.632 --> 13:23.924
NO. NOT AT ALL.

13:23.924 --> 13:24.885
COME ON IN.

13:27.017 --> 13:30.060
[ SIGHS ]
HOW'S STEVIE?

13:30.060 --> 13:32.392
THE GRAYSONS
REALLY HURT HER.

13:35.485 --> 13:37.817
JACK, I'M SO SORRY.

13:37.817 --> 13:38.818
I KNOW.

13:41.531 --> 13:43.653
I GUESS THAT'S WHY I CAME.

13:43.653 --> 13:44.824
[ CHUCKLES ]

13:44.824 --> 13:46.947
I NEEDED TO SEE SOMEONE
WHO GETS IT.

13:53.333 --> 13:55.545
SO, THIS IS YOUR NEW TARGET?
 YES.

13:55.545 --> 13:57.377
LUKE GILLIAM.

13:57.377 --> 14:01.341
HE RUNS A CLEAN GAS COMPANY,
BUT IT'S A SHAM.

14:01.341 --> 14:03.803
THE CHEMICALS HE USES
ARE TOXIC.

14:03.803 --> 14:07.517
THEY GET INTO THE WATER,
POISON THE GROUND.

14:07.517 --> 14:09.519
AND LET ME GUESS --
HIS WELLS DON'T END UP

14:09.519 --> 14:12.562
IN TOWNS LIKE THE HAMPTONS.
 NO, THESE PEOPLE DON'T HAVE
THE MEANS TO FIGHT BACK.

14:12.562 --> 14:14.024
THIS GUY
HAS BEEN UNTOUCHABLE.

14:14.024 --> 14:17.437
HE HAS EVIDENCE
OF CONRAD'S ROLE IN THE BOMBING.

14:17.437 --> 14:19.069
I'M MEETING WITH HIM
TOMORROW.

14:19.069 --> 14:20.360
SO, GETTING TO THIS GUY

14:20.360 --> 14:22.532
WILL HELP YOU TAKE DOWN
THE GRAYSONS?

14:22.532 --> 14:24.744
YEAH.

14:24.744 --> 14:26.366
[ SIGHS ]

14:26.366 --> 14:27.617
YOU KNOW,
MAYBE THERE'S SOMETHING

14:27.617 --> 14:29.039
THAT YOU COULD DO TO HELP.

14:29.039 --> 14:31.161
REALLY?

14:31.161 --> 14:34.414
LOOK, YOU KNOW I DON'T LIKE YOU
INVOLVED IN ANY OF THIS --

14:34.414 --> 14:35.545
BUT I AM.

14:35.545 --> 14:37.547
ESPECIALLY AFTER WHAT HAPPENED
TO MY MOM.

14:39.629 --> 14:41.381
I'M ALL IN.

14:41.381 --> 14:43.924
LET'S DO THIS.

14:53.273 --> 14:55.685
WHY EXACTLY
AM I WAITING HERE?

14:55.685 --> 14:58.728
YOU CAN'T HAVE A STAKEOUT
WITHOUT TAKEOUT.

14:58.728 --> 15:01.281
OH.

15:01.281 --> 15:04.284
DO YOU HAVE A LEAD
ON OSCAR CHAPMAN OR NOT?

15:04.284 --> 15:06.366
♪ TA-DA! ♪

15:06.366 --> 15:09.119
WHAT?
CHAPMAN LIVES THERE?

15:09.119 --> 15:13.583
NO. BUT A WOMAN
NAMED BRENDA EVANS DOES.

15:13.583 --> 15:16.496
SHE EMPTIED OUT
OSCAR CHAPMAN'S BANK ACCOUNT

15:16.496 --> 15:20.170
WITH A BUNCH OF FAKE I.D.s
20 YEARS AGO.

15:20.170 --> 15:22.802
Aiden: SO, EITHER THIS WOMAN
STOLE FROM CHAPMAN,

15:22.802 --> 15:24.134
OR SHE'S WORKING WITH HIM.

15:24.134 --> 15:25.045
EXACTLY.

15:25.045 --> 15:27.137
WHICH MAKES HER

15:27.137 --> 15:29.179
OUR BEST BET
AT FINDING HIM.

15:29.179 --> 15:30.470
[ SIGHS ]

15:31.931 --> 15:33.683
WHY THE AIDEN FACE?

15:33.683 --> 15:35.055
THIS IS GOOD NEWS.

15:36.766 --> 15:40.900
I THOUGHT THINGS WERE BETTER
AFTER YOUR TRIP HOME.

15:40.900 --> 15:42.692
WELL, WITH MY MOTHER, YES,
BUT, THEN AGAIN,

15:42.692 --> 15:44.064
SHE DIDN'T PLANT A BOMB
ON A PLANE

15:44.064 --> 15:46.486
THAT KILLED OVER 200 PEOPLE,
NOW, DID SHE, NOLAN?

15:46.486 --> 15:49.409
AIDEN, WE DON'T KNOW
THE WHOLE TRUTH.

15:49.409 --> 15:53.123
I MEAN, HE TRIED TO TALK
TO A REPORTER, RIGHT?

15:53.123 --> 15:55.455
WHAT, TO SELL HIS STORY,
REWRITE HISTORY?

15:55.455 --> 15:57.127
I MEAN,
WHICH ONE OF THOSE

15:57.127 --> 15:59.839
IS MEANT TO MAKE ME
FEEL BETTER, EH, NOLAN?

15:59.839 --> 16:04.214
HE WASN'T DAVID CLARKE.
HE WAS A COWARD.

16:06.086 --> 16:07.507
HELLO?

16:09.389 --> 16:11.761
[ DOOR CLOSES ]

16:14.394 --> 16:17.897
IS SOMETHING WRONG?

16:17.897 --> 16:19.519
I SPOKE WITH CONRAD.

16:20.900 --> 16:22.022
IS IT TRUE?

16:22.022 --> 16:25.405
DID YOU PROFIT
OFF OF DAVID'S DEATH?

16:25.405 --> 16:27.817
I DON'T HAVE TO EXPLAIN
MYSELF.

16:27.817 --> 16:30.450
I DON'T WANT TO,
AND I DON'T HAVE TO.

16:30.450 --> 16:33.743
YOU DAMN WELL BETTER
EXPLAIN YOURSELF NOW.

16:36.746 --> 16:40.580
I NEED TO KNOW THE TRUTH.

16:40.580 --> 16:43.463
I CARRIED THIS GUILT
FOR 20 YEARS,

16:43.463 --> 16:46.336
AND EVERY TIME
I LOOKED AT CONRAD,

16:46.336 --> 16:50.300
I WAS FORCED TO REMEMBER
THE CHOICE I HAD TO MAKE.

16:50.300 --> 16:54.013
AND NOW HE TELLS ME
THAT YOU'RE PART OF IT.

16:56.186 --> 16:58.017
I CAN'T LIVE LIKE THIS.

17:00.900 --> 17:01.731
STOP IT.

17:01.731 --> 17:02.692
WILL YOU STOP?!

17:02.692 --> 17:04.694
STOP IT!
 DAMN YOU!

17:04.694 --> 17:07.107
CONRAD WANTS THIS.

17:07.107 --> 17:08.647
DON'T GIVE HIM THAT POWER.

17:08.647 --> 17:11.241
HE'S TRYING TO DRIVE US APART.
DON'T YOU SEE?

17:17.117 --> 17:20.579
I WAS BROUGHT
AS AN INVESTOR.

17:20.579 --> 17:24.002
I HAD NOTHING TO DO
WITH IT.

17:24.002 --> 17:27.877
A REPORTER WANTED TO REVEAL
THE STORY ABOUT DAVID.

17:27.877 --> 17:30.970
THAT WOULD HAVE
BADLY EXPOSED CONRAD.

17:30.970 --> 17:35.265
AND I KNEW IF CONRAD WENT DOWN,
HE'D TAKE YOU WITH HIM.

17:37.056 --> 17:40.480
SO, I SILENCED THE STORY.

17:40.480 --> 17:42.982
BECAUSE I LOVE YOU.

17:42.982 --> 17:46.276
I ALWAYS LOVED YOU.

17:51.111 --> 17:54.244
CONRAD
WILL KEEP COMING AT US...

17:54.244 --> 17:56.196
UNLESS WE STOP HIM.

17:56.196 --> 17:57.657
I KNOW.

18:00.079 --> 18:03.082
THERE IS SOMETHING
I COULD DO,

18:03.082 --> 18:06.166
BUT IT'S NOT
WITHOUT RISK.

18:08.418 --> 18:10.170
TO BE HONEST,
MISS THORNE,

18:10.170 --> 18:12.172
I'M SURPRISED
YOU'RE LOOKING FOR A JOB.

18:12.172 --> 18:15.014
BUT MY DIVORCE LEFT ME
STRUGGLING.

18:15.014 --> 18:17.307
YOU WERE SCREWED
BY THE GRAYSONS.

18:17.307 --> 18:19.639
TRUST ME,
I KNOW HOW THEY OPERATE.

18:19.639 --> 18:21.981
THAT'S RIGHT.
YOU WORKED FOR CONRAD.

18:23.313 --> 18:25.605
WELL, I WOULD LOVE TO BE A PART
OF WHAT YOU'RE DOING NOW.

18:25.605 --> 18:27.567
I HAVE SERVED ON MANY BOARDS
IN THE GREEN SECTOR,

18:27.567 --> 18:30.320
AND MAYBE I COULD HELP
SMOOTH OVER SOME OF THE PROBLEMS

18:30.320 --> 18:31.861
YOU'RE HAVING
WITH ENVIRONMENTALISTS.

18:31.861 --> 18:34.494
[ CHUCKLES ]
THEY'RE ECO-TERRORISTS.

18:34.494 --> 18:37.827
OH, NO, I'VE SPENT A FORTUNE
DEFENDING MYSELF.

18:37.827 --> 18:40.119
BELIEVE ME,
I'M THE VICTIM HERE.

18:40.119 --> 18:41.741
YOU'RE FULL OF CRAP.

18:43.082 --> 18:45.505
I GOT FAMILY THAT LIVES NEAR
ONE OF YOUR WELLS.

18:45.505 --> 18:48.248
THE GROUND IS POISONED.
PEOPLE CAN'T DRINK THE WATER.

18:48.248 --> 18:50.250
THIS IS WHAT
I'M TALKING ABOUT.

18:50.250 --> 18:51.341
HEY!

18:53.303 --> 18:55.385
HOW DO YOU
LIVE WITH YOURSELF?

18:58.308 --> 19:02.522
I CARRY THESE AROUND
TO SHOW PEOPLE LIKE YOU.

19:02.522 --> 19:05.144
THIS IS THE COMPOUND
MY COMPANY USES

19:05.144 --> 19:08.478
TO EXTRACT GAS
FROM THE GROUND.

19:08.478 --> 19:11.731
AND THIS IS HOW DANGEROUS
IT IS.

19:15.074 --> 19:17.036
SO, I THINK
WHAT WE'VE LEARNED HERE

19:17.036 --> 19:20.119
IS THAT YOU DON'T KNOW
WHAT YOU'RE TALKING ABOUT.

19:20.119 --> 19:22.492
YOU'VE GOT AN ANSWER
FOR EVERYTHING, DON'T YOU?

19:22.492 --> 19:24.083
EXCUSE ME,
BUT YOU'RE WRONG.

19:24.083 --> 19:26.416
MR. GILLIAM HAS WON

19:26.416 --> 19:28.958
EVERY SINGLE CASE
EVER BROUGHT AGAINST HIM.

19:28.958 --> 19:31.251
THAT'S 30 TRIALS
IN 12 STATES,

19:31.251 --> 19:32.922
SO MAYBE YOU SHOULD DIG
A LITTLE DEEPER

19:32.922 --> 19:35.345
THAN LIBERAL PROPAGANDA BEFORE
YOU ATTACK SOMEONE'S CHARACTER.

19:39.469 --> 19:42.222
I'M SORRY
FOR JUMPING IN.

19:42.222 --> 19:46.065
BUT...I'M A BIG PROPONENT
OF DOING YOUR RESEARCH.

19:46.065 --> 19:47.307
AND I'M IMPRESSED.

19:47.307 --> 19:49.018
I'D LIKE YOU TO COME
TO THE AWARDS TOMORROW.

19:49.018 --> 19:51.691
THE LOCALS SEEM RESTLESS,

19:51.691 --> 19:54.153
AND I COULD USE SOMEONE LIKE YOU
IN MY CORNER.

19:55.615 --> 19:59.239
WELL, THERE'S NOWHERE
I'D RATHER BE.

19:59.239 --> 20:01.200
WE'RE SO PLEASED
YOU COULD COME.

20:01.200 --> 20:03.202
AND WITHOUT
YOUR MONITOR.

20:03.202 --> 20:05.164
YEAH,
I'M A LITTLE CONFUSED.

20:05.164 --> 20:07.377
I WAS SUPPOSED TO BE
ON HOUSE ARREST

20:07.377 --> 20:09.249
FOR ANOTHER SIX MONTHS.

20:09.249 --> 20:11.000
YEAH, YEAH,
I CALLED IN A FEW FAVORS

20:11.000 --> 20:12.752
AND GOT THE TERMS
OF YOUR PAROLE CHANGED.

20:12.752 --> 20:14.003
[ CHUCKLES ]

20:14.003 --> 20:15.885
WHAT DID I TELL YOU
ABOUT MY BROTHER?

20:15.885 --> 20:17.216
LISTEN, JAVIER,
IT'S NO SECRET

20:17.216 --> 20:19.098
WHY WE WANTED YOU
TO COME IN TODAY.

20:19.098 --> 20:22.181
YOU REPRESENT A NEW FRONTIER
IN MEDIA TECHNOLOGY.

20:22.181 --> 20:24.394
AND WE HAVE THE RESOURCES
TO LAUNCH

20:24.394 --> 20:27.106
BOTH YOU AND YOUR PRODUCT
AT THE SAME TIME.

20:27.106 --> 20:29.939
JAVIER,
WE CAN MAKE YOU A STAR.

20:32.312 --> 20:35.315
[ LAUGHS ]

20:35.315 --> 20:38.698
THIS CAN CHANGE YOUR LIFE,
JAVIER.

20:38.698 --> 20:40.239
THIS IS AMAZING.

20:40.239 --> 20:42.572
I'M BLOWN AWAY, GUYS.

20:42.572 --> 20:44.243
SERIOUSLY.
I JUST --

20:44.243 --> 20:47.126
I KNOW.
YOU MADE A PROMISE TO NOLAN.

20:47.126 --> 20:49.168
YES.

20:49.168 --> 20:50.750
AND YOUR LOYALTY
IS HONORABLE.

20:50.750 --> 20:52.502
BUT THIS
IS A BUSINESS DECISION,

20:52.502 --> 20:55.795
AND YOU MUST CONSIDER
ALL YOUR OPTIONS.

20:55.795 --> 20:57.717
WHY DON'T YOU THINK ABOUT IT
ON YOUR TEST DRIVE?

21:00.179 --> 21:03.092
THIS IS A KEY
TO A McLAREN.

21:04.093 --> 21:07.096
HOW DID YOU KNOW
THAT'S MY FAVORITE CAR?
 I ASKED YOUR PROGRAM.

21:07.096 --> 21:09.058
OH, OF COURSE YOU DID.

21:09.058 --> 21:11.060
WHY DON'T YOU GO SEE
WHAT SHE CAN DO, HUH?
 YEAH.

21:11.060 --> 21:13.192
HELL, YEAH!

21:13.192 --> 21:14.894
THANK YOU.

21:14.894 --> 21:15.985
THANK YOU.

21:15.985 --> 21:17.066
HAVE FUN.

21:27.407 --> 21:29.078
BRENDA EVANS?
 YES?

21:29.078 --> 21:32.001
WE'D LIKE TO ASK YOU
A FEW QUESTIONS

21:32.001 --> 21:33.753
ABOUT OSCAR CHAPMAN.

21:37.046 --> 21:38.418
[ ELECTRICITY BUZZES ]

21:38.418 --> 21:39.839
AH!

21:39.839 --> 21:41.300
[ GROANS ]

21:43.182 --> 21:45.885
[ TIRES SCREECH, HORN HONKS ]

21:48.598 --> 21:49.479
[ GRUNTS ]

21:57.026 --> 21:58.818
MY GOD,
YOU'RE OSCAR CHAPMAN.

22:04.574 --> 22:07.907
I-I DIDN'T REALIZE
WHO YOU BOTH WERE.

22:07.907 --> 22:10.660
I THOUGHT YOU WERE HERE
TO KILL ME.

22:10.660 --> 22:13.042
I-I'M VERY SORRY,
MR. ROSS.

22:13.042 --> 22:14.544
[ GRUNTS ]
IT'S NO PROBLEM.

22:14.544 --> 22:17.086
I ALWAYS FOUND
THE USE OF BOTH ARMS REDUNDANT.

22:17.086 --> 22:18.418
HOW DID YOU FIND ME?

22:18.418 --> 22:19.719
WE HAVE OUR WAYS...

22:19.719 --> 22:22.011
BRENDA?

22:22.011 --> 22:24.964
I'M ONLY HER
WHEN I LEAVE HOME.

22:24.964 --> 22:28.307
THE PEOPLE I'M HIDING FROM HAVE
NEVER STOPPED LOOKING FOR ME.

22:28.307 --> 22:30.470
SO, I GUESS
IT'S NO SURPRISE

22:30.470 --> 22:33.523
THAT TREVOR MATHIS' SON
DIDN'T STOP, EITHER.

22:33.523 --> 22:35.064
HOW DO YOU KNOW
MY FATHER?

22:35.064 --> 22:36.606
I'D JUST MOVED TO LONDON,

22:36.606 --> 22:39.238
AND HE CAME TO ME
WITH THE STORY OF A LIFETIME.

22:39.238 --> 22:43.112
WHY YOU
AND NOT THE POLICE?

22:43.112 --> 22:44.694
WELL, HE DIDN'T KNOW
WHO HE COULD TRUST.

22:44.694 --> 22:46.576
HE HAD ALREADY
BEEN LIED TO ONCE

22:46.576 --> 22:48.618
WHEN THEY TOLD HIM
THAT THEY'D --

22:48.618 --> 22:51.200
THEY'D FREE YOUR SISTER
IF HE PLANTED THAT BOMB.

22:51.200 --> 22:52.331
BUT I DON'T UNDERSTAND.

22:52.331 --> 22:54.083
WHY WOULD HE LET
ALL THOSE PEOPLE DIE?

22:54.083 --> 22:58.958
YOUR FATHER HAD NO IDEA
WHAT HE PLANTED ON THAT PLANE.

22:58.958 --> 23:01.050
THEY TOLD HIM
IT WAS DIAMONDS.

23:01.050 --> 23:03.463
WHEN WE MET,
HE CARRIED SO MUCH SHAME.

23:03.463 --> 23:06.175
HAVING TO HIDE THAT FROM YOU
AND YOUR MOTHER CONSUMED HIM.

23:06.175 --> 23:08.097
HE WAS DESPERATE
TO MAKE THINGS RIGHT.

23:08.097 --> 23:10.179
THEN WHY KILL HIMSELF?

23:10.179 --> 23:12.391
I'M SORRY.

23:15.475 --> 23:17.016
YOUR FATHER WAS MURDERED.

23:19.569 --> 23:22.191
HE HAD EVERY INTENTION
OF FACING WHAT HE DID.

23:22.191 --> 23:26.025
BUT MR. LeMARCHAL
HAD OTHER IDEAS.

23:26.025 --> 23:29.198
YEAH, THE SECOND I GAVE PASCAL
THAT -- THAT STORY,

23:29.198 --> 23:30.790
I KNEW I'D MADE A MISTAKE.

23:30.790 --> 23:32.832
AND, SO,
I-I CALLED YOUR DAD,

23:32.832 --> 23:35.665
AND I TOLD HIM TO COLLECT
EVERYTHING HE COULD

23:35.665 --> 23:38.167
AND TO MEET ME,
BUT HE NEVER SHOWED.

23:38.167 --> 23:41.040
AND WHEN I HEARD
ABOUT THAT SUICIDE,

23:41.040 --> 23:44.754
I KNEW PASCAL HAD STAGED
THAT WHOLE THING.

23:44.754 --> 23:46.716
HE KILLED YOUR FATHER.

23:52.261 --> 23:55.685
WE NEED YOU TO COME FORWARD,
MR. CHAPMAN.

23:55.685 --> 23:58.978
WE CAN HELP YOU
GET YOUR LIFE BACK --

23:58.978 --> 24:00.650
YOUR REAL LIFE.

24:00.650 --> 24:06.155
BUT ONLY
IF YOU STOP HIDING.

24:06.155 --> 24:08.277
PLEASE...

24:10.199 --> 24:12.622
HELP ME FINISH
MY FATHER'S FIGHT.

24:15.955 --> 24:18.127
I'LL DO WHATEVER YOU NEED.

24:21.380 --> 24:23.753
OH...

24:23.753 --> 24:25.004
PHEW.

24:25.004 --> 24:26.215
[ LAUGHS ]

24:28.087 --> 24:29.929
THIS ROOM IS, UH...

24:29.929 --> 24:34.223
IT'S BIGGER THAN THE APARTMENT
 BUILDING THAT I GREW UP IN.

24:34.223 --> 24:35.224
[ LAUGHS ]

24:35.224 --> 24:36.395
OH, NOT THERE!

24:36.395 --> 24:39.358
THAT WOULD BE LIKE BREAKING
50 MIRRORS.

24:39.358 --> 24:41.651
I DO NOT CARE.

24:41.651 --> 24:47.066
I FEEL INVINCIBLE
WITH YOU BY MY SIDE.

24:47.066 --> 24:48.698
DOES THAT MEAN
YOU'LL SIGN?

24:54.113 --> 24:56.075
I CAN'T BETRAY NOLAN.

24:56.075 --> 24:57.376
WE'RE MORE
THAN JUST FRIENDS.

24:57.376 --> 24:58.788
WE...

24:59.919 --> 25:01.581
WE'RE BROTHERS.

25:01.581 --> 25:03.543
YOU ONLY KNEW HIM
BEHIND BARS.

25:03.543 --> 25:05.545
BUT OUT HERE, HE'LL DO
WHATEVER IT TAKES TO WIN.

25:05.545 --> 25:07.506
THAT'S WHY HE STUCK YOU
WITH THAT CRAPPY DEAL.

25:07.506 --> 25:09.218
LOOK, I'M SURE
HE'S GONNA CHANGE IT.

25:09.218 --> 25:12.181
HE WANTS TO TAKE YOUR IDEAS
AND SHOVE YOU IN THE BACKGROUND.

25:13.262 --> 25:14.393
HEY.

25:19.228 --> 25:22.732
YOU CAN EITHER BE
NEXT TO NOLAN ROSS,

25:22.732 --> 25:26.445
OR YOU CAN BE
THE NEXT NOLAN ROSS.

25:29.198 --> 25:31.110
[ SIREN WAILS ]

25:31.110 --> 25:32.491
CHAPMAN'S AGREED
TO HELP US.

25:32.491 --> 25:34.073
THAT'S GREAT.

25:34.073 --> 25:36.576
WELL, WE'VE MADE
SOME GOOD PROGRESS, TOO.

25:36.576 --> 25:38.578
SO TAKE YOUR TIME.

25:38.578 --> 25:39.869
AND, AIDEN...

25:39.869 --> 25:41.370
I'M HAPPY FOR YOU.

25:43.252 --> 25:44.503
[ CELLPHONE BEEPS ]

25:44.503 --> 25:46.876
[ SIGHS ]

25:48.878 --> 25:51.050
SO, HE'S, UH,
BACK IN THE PICTURE?

25:53.092 --> 25:54.724
WELL,
IT'S COMPLICATED.

25:54.724 --> 25:56.135
[ CHUCKLES ]

25:56.135 --> 25:57.977
SAY NO MORE.

25:57.977 --> 25:59.769
I KNOW ALL ABOUT
COMPLICATED.

26:01.601 --> 26:06.145
SO, I'M ASSUMING THIS ISN'T
WHAT GILLIAM USES IN HIS MINES.

26:06.145 --> 26:08.778
IT'S A MIXTURE OF SALINE
AND GELATIN.

26:08.778 --> 26:10.740
SO HE'S LYING
TO EVERYONE.

26:12.191 --> 26:15.905
WELL, YOU CAN USE THAT,
RIGHT?

26:20.409 --> 26:22.251
WHAT'S ON HERE?

26:22.251 --> 26:23.703
HIS UNDOING.

26:26.585 --> 26:28.207
[ KNOCK ON DOOR ]

26:30.970 --> 26:32.972
[ CHUCKLES ]

26:32.972 --> 26:36.055
I HAD A FEELING
YOU'D BE STOPPING BY.

26:36.055 --> 26:38.638
IF MEMORY SERVES,

26:38.638 --> 26:42.271
ARMAGNAC IS YOUR ELIXIR
OF CHOICE FOR A BROKEN HEART.

26:42.271 --> 26:46.065
YOU KNOW, I WISH I COULD SAY
THAT I WAS SORRY,

26:46.065 --> 26:50.229
BUT WE BOTH KNOW
FEW SOUNDS ARE SWEETER

26:50.229 --> 26:52.611
THAN THE CRUMBLING
OF YOUR FELLOW MAN.

26:53.693 --> 26:55.034
[ CELLPHONE BEEPS ]

26:55.034 --> 26:56.575
I HAVE EVERYTHING HANDLED.

26:56.575 --> 26:58.157
THERE WON'T BE ANY FALLOUT.

26:58.157 --> 27:01.741
JUST STAY CALM,
 AND IT'LL ALL BE FINE.

27:01.741 --> 27:04.163
[ CELLPHONE BEEPS ]

27:04.163 --> 27:07.747
DO YOU RECALL OUR CHATS
FROM 1993?

27:07.747 --> 27:10.339
SO, THAT'S WHAT YOU HAVE
ON ME.

27:12.011 --> 27:14.633
YOU RECORDED
OUR CONVERSATIONS.

27:14.633 --> 27:20.059
ABOUT THE BOMB,
DAVID --

27:20.059 --> 27:21.640
EVERY WORD.

27:21.640 --> 27:24.643
YOU'RE ON THOSE TAPES,
TOO.

27:24.643 --> 27:26.605
BUT I CONTROL
WHAT THE WORLD HEARS...

27:28.067 --> 27:30.439
...WHICH MEANS...

27:30.439 --> 27:33.322
I CONTROL YOU.

27:45.584 --> 27:47.166
[ DOOR CLOSES ]

27:55.174 --> 27:56.595
YOU OKAY?

27:58.387 --> 27:59.799
YEAH.

27:59.799 --> 28:02.011
YEAH, I THINK I AM.

28:02.011 --> 28:04.013
'CAUSE, UH...

28:04.013 --> 28:07.016
I KNOW A LITTLE BIT
ABOUT UNRESOLVED FATHER ISSUES

28:07.016 --> 28:10.399
AN, UH, HOW IT FEELS
TO GET PAST THEM.

28:13.402 --> 28:15.404
HOW ABOUT A HUG,
BIG GUY?

28:17.156 --> 28:18.407
[ CAMERA SHUTTER CLICKING ]

28:19.488 --> 28:21.620
OR NOT.

28:28.087 --> 28:30.089
I ASSUME YOUR DILIGENCE
WITH THAT NEW DEAL

28:30.089 --> 28:33.252
HAS SOMETHING TO DO WITH THE BOY
CHARLOTTE BROUGHT HOME.

28:33.252 --> 28:36.255
I HAVE TO SAY, DANIEL, I DON'T
LIKE YOU USING YOUR SISTER.

28:36.255 --> 28:39.839
OH, I'M NOT.
SHE DOES WHAT SHE WANTS.

28:39.839 --> 28:42.051
AND I ACTUALLY THINK
SHE LIKES HIM.

28:42.051 --> 28:43.642
HE'S A FELON.

28:44.764 --> 28:47.306
THEN HE SHOULD FIT
RIGHT IN.

28:48.437 --> 28:50.229
I NOTICED THESE
LYING AROUND.

28:50.229 --> 28:55.024
ISN'T THIS THE GUY YOU HAD
THE DUST-UP WITH AT THE TRACK?

28:55.024 --> 28:56.195
WHAT'S HIS STORY?

28:58.027 --> 28:59.989
LUKE GILLIAM USED TO WORK
WITH YOUR FATHER.

28:59.989 --> 29:03.572
WAS HE INVOLVED
WITH THE, UH...?

29:06.285 --> 29:09.128
I HAVE A MAJOR DEAL
ABOUT TO CLOSE.

29:09.128 --> 29:11.460
TELL ME NOTHING IS ABOUT
TO BLOW BACK ON THIS FAMILY.

29:11.460 --> 29:13.252
OH, LUKE WON'T
BE A PROBLEM.

29:13.252 --> 29:14.333
HOW CAN YOU BE SO SURE?

29:14.333 --> 29:16.876
BECAUSE I BROUGHT HIM HERE.

29:18.137 --> 29:19.468
THAT FIGHT
WAS JUST FOR SHOW.

29:19.468 --> 29:21.090
WHO DO YOU THINK
NOMINATED HIM

29:21.090 --> 29:23.973
FOR THAT ABSURD AWARD
HE'S RECEIVING?

29:25.434 --> 29:26.685
WHAT ARE YOU UP TO?

29:26.685 --> 29:29.228
I'M MERELY
TESTING A THEORY.

29:29.228 --> 29:31.190
OH, SO,
THIS IS ABOUT EMILY?

29:31.190 --> 29:34.483
AND YOUR MANEUVER
TO STEAL NOLAN'S PROTéGé ISN'T?

29:36.235 --> 29:38.067
HAPPY HUNTING.

29:42.952 --> 29:45.825
AWARDS ARE A PLATFORM
TO HELP US SPREAD OUR MESSAGE.

29:45.825 --> 29:46.826
EXCUSE ME.

29:46.826 --> 29:49.538
EMILY,
GLAD YOU COULD MAKE IT.

29:49.538 --> 29:50.960
OH,
I WOULDN'T MISS IT.

29:50.960 --> 29:53.672
LISTEN, I'VE BEEN
GETTING A LOT OF TWEETS

29:53.672 --> 29:55.464
FROM OUR LOCAL
NATURE NUTS.

29:55.464 --> 29:58.677
CAN YOU RUN INTERFERENCE
IN CASE THINGS TAKE A TURN?

29:58.677 --> 30:00.509
ABSOLUTELY.

30:00.509 --> 30:02.761
JUST STICK TO YOUR PRESENTATION.
THAT'LL SHUT THEM UP.

30:02.761 --> 30:05.514
OH, NOTHING EVER STOPS PEOPLE
WITH AN AGENDA.

30:05.514 --> 30:07.306
VICTORIA?

30:07.306 --> 30:08.767
I DON'T BELIEVE IT.

30:08.767 --> 30:10.479
ONCE CAMERAS ARRIVE,

30:10.479 --> 30:13.692
OF COURSE YOU PUT ASIDE
YOUR RIGHTEOUS INDIGNATION.

30:13.692 --> 30:16.395
[ SCOFFS ]
HYPOCRISY IS ALIVE AND WELL

30:16.395 --> 30:17.566
AND LIVING IN THE HAMPTONS.

30:17.566 --> 30:19.358
WELL, WE'VE FINALLY
HIT UPON A SUBJECT

30:19.358 --> 30:20.569
ON WHICH
YOU'RE AN EXPERT.

30:20.569 --> 30:22.701
OH, YOU'RE NOT
ON THE GUEST LIST, VICKI,

30:22.701 --> 30:25.654
BUT I'M SURE WE CAN DRUM UP
SOMETHING FOR YOU...IN THE BACK.

30:27.867 --> 30:30.289
I WASN'T EXPECTING
TO SEE YOU HERE, VICTORIA.

30:30.289 --> 30:31.450
WELL, I CAN ONLY HOPE

30:31.450 --> 30:33.452
IT COMES AS A TERRIBLE
DISAPPOINTMENT TO YOU.

30:34.793 --> 30:36.545
[ CHUCKLES ]

30:39.458 --> 30:41.881
[ KEYBOARD CLACKING ]

30:45.965 --> 30:47.176
LOOKY. LOOKY.

30:48.347 --> 30:50.099
THIS CAME FROM MY LAWYERS.

30:50.099 --> 30:52.141
AND I THINK...

30:52.141 --> 30:55.144
YOU WILL BE HAPPY
WITH THE CHANGES.

30:55.144 --> 30:58.938
BUT I WANTED TO FIX
THE BUGS IN THE SOURCE CODE,

30:58.938 --> 31:01.480
AND I CAN'T FIND IT IN
THE CLOUD. DID YOU MOVE IT?

31:05.364 --> 31:07.366
HEY...

31:07.366 --> 31:08.697
WHERE'S YOUR MONITOR?

31:08.697 --> 31:10.619
MY PAROLE OFFICER
TOOK IT OFF.

31:12.161 --> 31:15.704
DANIEL GRAYSON
CALLED IN A FAVOR.

31:18.127 --> 31:23.052
THAT'S WHY MYCLONE
IS NOT ON THE SERVER.

31:23.052 --> 31:25.174
I DIDN'T THINK IT WOULD BE RIGHT
FOR YOU TO KEEP WORKING ON IT.

31:26.265 --> 31:28.557
JAVIER, LISTEN TO ME.

31:28.557 --> 31:30.769
THIS PROGRAM --
IT'S NOT READY.

31:30.769 --> 31:32.681
YOU --
YOU'RE NOT READY.

31:32.681 --> 31:35.604
YOU CANNOT GO INTO BUSINESS
WITH THESE PEOPLE.

31:35.604 --> 31:37.146
AND IT IS NOT
EVEN UP FOR DEBATE!

31:37.146 --> 31:38.938
IT NEVER IS WITH YOU,
IS IT?!

31:38.938 --> 31:41.941
IT'S ALWAYS GONNA BE
WHAT NOLAN ROSS WANTS.

31:41.941 --> 31:45.524
DANIEL AND MARGAUX --
THEY ARE LOOKING OUT FOR ME.

31:46.615 --> 31:48.237
YOU WILL REGRET THIS.

31:48.237 --> 31:50.199
[ SCOFFS ]

31:53.452 --> 31:55.294
NO ONE PLAYS ME.

31:55.294 --> 31:57.876
OH, BUT YOU'VE
ALREADY BEEN PLAYED.

32:03.632 --> 32:04.883
Luke:
BEFORE I TAKE MY LEAVE,

32:04.883 --> 32:06.845
I'D LIKE TO ADDRESS
THE ACTIVISTS OUT THERE

32:06.845 --> 32:09.258
WHO QUESTION MY INTEGRITY.

32:09.258 --> 32:12.681
I WANT THEM TO KNOW
I RUN THE CLEANEST, SAFEST,

32:12.681 --> 32:14.643
GREENEST COMPANY
ON THE PLANET,

32:14.643 --> 32:17.016
NOT BECAUSE IT'S GOOD BUSINESS,

32:17.016 --> 32:23.192
BUT BECAUSE I TRULY LOVE OUR
BEAUTIFUL MOTHER WE CALL EARTH.

32:23.192 --> 32:25.524
AND IF I CAN PUT THESE CHEMICALS
IN HER,

32:25.524 --> 32:30.909
YOU CAN BE DAMN SURE THEY'RE
SAFE ENOUGH TO PUT IN ME.

32:31.830 --> 32:33.622
[ APPLAUSE ]

32:38.787 --> 32:40.879
[ INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS ]

32:50.049 --> 32:51.680
OH, NO.

32:51.680 --> 32:54.853
[ COUGHS ]
 MR. GILLIAM,
ARE YOU ALL RIGHT?

32:54.853 --> 32:56.685
I NEED A DOCTOR NOW.

32:56.685 --> 32:58.267
I THOUGHT YOU SAID
THE FORMULA WAS SAFE.

32:58.267 --> 32:59.688
IT'S NOT, YOU IDIOT!

32:59.688 --> 33:01.860
[ WHEEZING ]

33:01.860 --> 33:03.062
[ SPECTATORS MURMUR ]

33:10.069 --> 33:12.281
[ SHATTER ]

33:14.663 --> 33:16.535
MR. LeMARCHAL,
I BEG OF YOU --

33:16.535 --> 33:19.788
DO YOU KNOW WHAT
YOUR PROBLEM ALWAYS WAS?

33:21.830 --> 33:23.542
YOU WERE TOO GOOD
A REPORTER.

33:23.542 --> 33:26.004
[ SCOFFS ]

33:38.517 --> 33:40.059
Reporter:
 ENVIRONMENTAL ACTIVISTS

33:40.059 --> 33:41.690
WELCOME THE REVELATIONS
 CAUGHT ON CAMERA

33:41.690 --> 33:43.602
THAT CONFIRM THE RUMORS
 THAT HAVE HOUNDED

33:43.602 --> 33:45.064
LUKE GILLIAM FOR YEARS.

33:45.064 --> 33:47.606
THE ONCE CELEBRATED
 GILLIAM NATURAL GAS COMPANY --

33:47.606 --> 33:50.409
[ Distorted voice ]
Luke Gilliam...

33:50.409 --> 33:52.361
we have unfinished business.

33:52.361 --> 33:53.572
WHAT THE...?

33:58.997 --> 34:00.869
YOU DID THIS TO ME.

34:00.869 --> 34:02.581
I COULD HAVE DIED!

34:02.581 --> 34:05.003
THE DRUG I USED
WAS HARMLESS.

34:05.003 --> 34:06.545
I NEED YOU ALIVE.

34:06.545 --> 34:08.337
What do you want
with me?

34:08.337 --> 34:11.469
THE LEVERAGE THAT YOU HAVE
ON CONRAD GRAYSON.

34:11.469 --> 34:13.302
I DON'T KNOW
WHAT YOU'RE TALKING ABOUT.

34:13.302 --> 34:14.303
LOOK AT WHERE YOU ARE.

34:14.303 --> 34:15.844
Do you really
want to lie to me?

34:15.844 --> 34:17.556
WHY WOULD I GIVE THAT UP
TO YOU?

34:17.556 --> 34:19.478
Because if you don't,

34:19.478 --> 34:22.731
I WILL MAKE EVERY DAY
OF YOUR LIFE HELL.

34:22.731 --> 34:26.735
I will make you pay for all of
the people that you've hurt --

34:26.735 --> 34:30.239
both now and in the past.

34:30.239 --> 34:31.530
And that's not a threat.

34:32.610 --> 34:35.154
IT'S A PROMISE.

34:35.154 --> 34:39.118
I'LL GIVE YOU
WHAT YOU WANT.

34:39.118 --> 34:43.001
BUT, PLEASE,
LEAVE ME ALONE.

34:50.088 --> 34:52.130
[ TELEPHONE RINGING ]

34:57.094 --> 34:58.637
MARGAUX?

35:02.221 --> 35:03.602
NOLAN CALLED ME.

35:03.602 --> 35:05.434
YEAH.

35:06.525 --> 35:09.688
WELL,
I GUESS HE MUST BE UPSET.

35:11.490 --> 35:13.532
SO, YOU DID
 SCREW HIM OVER.

35:13.532 --> 35:16.495
NO. DANIEL AND I
MADE A BETTER OFFER.

35:16.495 --> 35:18.577
IT WASN'T ABOUT MONEY
FOR NOLAN.

35:18.577 --> 35:20.449
HE WANTED TO HELP THAT KID,
BUT DANIEL...

35:20.449 --> 35:21.660
[ SCOFFS ]

35:21.660 --> 35:23.742
...WANTS TO USE HIM
LIKE HE USES EVERYONE...

35:25.294 --> 35:27.456
...INCLUDING YOU.

35:27.456 --> 35:30.008
ARE WE REALLY DOING THIS
AGAIN?

35:30.008 --> 35:31.800
I KNOW THAT YOU THINK DANIEL
IS YOUR FRIEND,

35:31.800 --> 35:33.011
BUT TRUST ME, HE'S NOT.

35:34.553 --> 35:37.216
HE GETS OFF ON DOING THIS TO US,
AND I WISH YOU COULD SEE THAT.

35:37.216 --> 35:39.678
I'VE WORKED ALL MY LIFE
TO GET HERE,

35:39.678 --> 35:41.680
AND IT'S FINALLY HAPPENING.

35:41.680 --> 35:43.522
I WISH
YOU COULD SEE THAT.

35:43.522 --> 35:45.474
I CAN'T,

35:45.474 --> 35:48.267
NOT WHEN MY FRIENDS
END UP YOUR COLLATERAL DAMAGE.

35:49.728 --> 35:51.570
JACK...

35:51.570 --> 35:54.573
JACK, DON'T LEAVE
LIKE THIS.

35:54.573 --> 35:56.865
PLEASE.

35:56.865 --> 35:58.447
[ SIGHS ]

36:01.450 --> 36:04.413
I LOVE YOU, MARGAUX, BUT RIGHT
NOW, I CAN'T BE AROUND YOU.

36:14.463 --> 36:16.425
Daniel: SO, I, UH --
I GOT YOU SOMETHING.

36:17.886 --> 36:19.508
A BENTLEY?

36:19.508 --> 36:23.512
THINK OF IT AS A FINDER'S FEE
FOR DELIVERING JAVIER.

36:23.512 --> 36:24.893
NO, I DIDN'T DO THIS
FOR A CAR.

36:24.893 --> 36:26.645
I JUST WANT WHAT'S BEST
FOR JAVIER.

36:26.645 --> 36:28.517
OKAY, WELL,
GIVE IT BACK, THEN.
 NO WAY!

36:28.517 --> 36:29.518
[ BOTH LAUGHING ]

36:29.518 --> 36:31.069
[ BOTH GASP ]

36:36.945 --> 36:38.867
I'M SORRY.

36:38.867 --> 36:40.239
DID I INTERRUPT?

36:40.239 --> 36:42.120
ARE YOU
OUT OF YOUR MIND?

36:42.120 --> 36:43.492
NO.

36:43.492 --> 36:46.785
BUT YOU MUST BE
FOR PISSING OFF A GENIUS.

36:46.785 --> 36:48.627
WOW.
I KNEW YOU WERE A LOSER.

36:48.627 --> 36:49.998
I DIDN'T KNOW
YOU WERE A SORE ONE.

36:49.998 --> 36:54.172
AH, YOU MAY HAVE INFECTED
MARGAUX AND THIS ONE,

36:54.172 --> 36:57.636
BUT I WON'T LET YOU
DO THE SAME TO JAVIER.

36:57.636 --> 37:00.599
I JUST WANT YOU
TO UNDERSTAND --

37:00.599 --> 37:03.181
THIS IS...WAR.

37:11.650 --> 37:13.442
[ INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS ]

37:18.487 --> 37:20.449
Conrad:
MR. MATHIS?

37:22.531 --> 37:24.413
SURPRISED?

37:24.413 --> 37:27.576
SURELY YOU MUST KNOW
I KEEP TRACK OF ALL THE PIECES

37:27.576 --> 37:28.917
ON THE BOARD.

37:28.917 --> 37:31.500
WHAT DO YOU WANT?

37:31.500 --> 37:33.922
THAT'S NOT
THE RIGHT QUESTION.

37:33.922 --> 37:35.924
IT'S WHAT YOU WANT --

37:35.924 --> 37:37.546
PASCAL LeMARCHAL.

37:37.546 --> 37:40.639
I ASSUME YOUR RETURN
ON THE HEELS OF HIS ARRIVAL

37:40.639 --> 37:41.840
WAS NO COINCIDENCE.

37:41.840 --> 37:45.263
YOU'VE LEARNED
THE TRUTH ABOUT HIM.

37:45.263 --> 37:46.845
WELL,
WHY DON'T YOU TELL ME?

37:46.845 --> 37:49.097
YOU SEEM ENLIGHTENED
ON THESE THINGS.

37:49.097 --> 37:52.481
WHILE YOU, ON THE OTHER HAND,
ARE FUMBLING THROUGH THE DARK.

37:52.481 --> 37:56.985
I'M AFRAID PASCAL HAS ALREADY
PAID A VISIT TO MR. CHAPMAN.

38:03.782 --> 38:06.325
HE'S CLEANING HOUSE,

38:06.325 --> 38:08.827
AND YOU'RE NEXT UNLESS
I RUN INTERFERENCE FOR YOU.

38:08.827 --> 38:10.208
AND WHY WOULD YOU DO THAT?

38:10.208 --> 38:12.170
WELL, BECAUSE
HE HAS SOMETHING I WANT,

38:12.170 --> 38:13.622
AND I BELIEVE
YOU CAN GET IT.

38:13.622 --> 38:15.834
GO TO HELL.

38:15.834 --> 38:19.628
YOU WILL FIND THAT IT'S BETTER
TO MAKE AN ALLY OF ME

38:19.628 --> 38:21.590
THAN AN ENEMY,
MR. MATHIS.

38:32.100 --> 38:33.732
IS THIS GUY
GOING TO BE A PROBLEM?

38:33.732 --> 38:37.275
NO, IN THE END, HE'LL DO
WHAT I WANT, MR. MARINO...

38:37.275 --> 38:38.737
JUST AS PASCAL DID,

38:38.737 --> 38:41.570
ONCE WE ALERTED HIM TO
THE WHEREABOUTS OF MR. CHAPMAN.

38:45.944 --> 38:48.867
Emily: LUKE GILLIAM HAD
THE MONEY TRANSFERS
FROM THE TERRORISTS.

38:48.867 --> 38:52.290
IT PROVES THAT CONRAD
WAS THE ORIGINAL CONTACT.

38:52.290 --> 38:55.083
SO, THIS -- THIS IS ALL
THE EVIDENCE YOU NEED?

38:55.083 --> 38:57.085
NO, THIS ONLY PROVES
CONRAD'S INVOLVEMENT.

38:57.085 --> 38:59.878
I MEAN, I-IT DOESN'T CLEAR
MY FATHER'S NAME,

38:59.878 --> 39:02.631
BUT [SIGHS]
I'M GETTING CLOSE.

39:04.342 --> 39:07.386
LOOK, I'M GLAD
THAT YOU STOPPED THAT GUY

39:07.386 --> 39:11.229
FROM HURTING OTHER PEOPLE,
BUT WATCH OUT FOR YOURSELF, TOO.

39:11.229 --> 39:13.472
DEAL.

39:15.313 --> 39:18.477
ALL RIGHT, WELL,
I GOT TO GET BACK TO CARL.

39:23.572 --> 39:25.944
OH, AND GOOD LUCK
ON THE BIG MOVE WITH MARGAUX.

39:27.986 --> 39:30.409
UH, UM...

39:32.200 --> 39:34.413
ACTUALLY, I'M NOT SO SURE
THAT'S GOING TO HAPPEN ANYMORE.

39:34.413 --> 39:35.704
WHAT?

39:36.795 --> 39:38.797
IN FACT,
I DON'T, UH...

39:40.799 --> 39:42.421
I DON'T THINK
WE'RE GONNA MAKE IT.

39:43.502 --> 39:44.963
YOU OKAY?

39:44.963 --> 39:46.555
YEAH.

39:49.558 --> 39:51.430
YEAH. I AM.

39:53.892 --> 39:55.474
GOOD NIGHT.
 GOOD NIGHT.

39:59.688 --> 40:01.900
[ SIGHS ]

40:01.900 --> 40:04.322
ALLIANCES CAN REUNITE
 OLD FRIENDS

40:04.322 --> 40:06.485
IN THE MOST UNEXPECTED
 OF WAYS...

40:10.158 --> 40:14.453
...BY TESTING THE BONDS
 THAT ARE THE STRONGEST OF ALL.

40:32.180 --> 40:35.393
THEY CAN LEAD
TO THE GREATEST OF VICTORIES...

40:37.105 --> 40:40.188
...OR TO YOUR ULTIMATE DEFEAT.

40:44.563 --> 40:47.405
NONE OF THIS WAS CHANCE.

40:47.405 --> 40:48.446
IT WAS EMILY.

40:48.446 --> 40:52.621
IMAGINE HIDING YOUR LIFE AWAY.

40:52.621 --> 40:57.496
ALL THIS TIME, I THOUGHT SHE
WAS WAGING WAR ON OUR FAMILY.

40:57.496 --> 40:59.498
BUT THIS GOES MUCH FARTHER.

41:02.501 --> 41:04.503
IT'S REVENGE...

41:06.675 --> 41:08.797
...FOR DAVID.
